For purposes of this section, “personal information” and “sensitive personal information” have the meanings given in the California Consumer Privacy Act of 2018 (as amended by the California Privacy Rights Act of 2020) (“
CCPA
”), and respectively include the terms “personal data” and “sensitive data” as defined in the Colorado Privacy Act (“
